      <title>Arctic Sovereignty and Security: Updating Our Ideas</title>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Mar 2016 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>Wilfrid Greaves and P. Whitney Lackenbauer</author>
      <link>https://www.newsdeeply.com/arctic/community/2016/03/23/arctic-sovereignty-and-security-updating-our-ideas</link>
      <guid>https://www.newsdeeply.com/arctic/community/2016/03/23/arctic-sovereignty-and-security-updating-our-ideas</guid>
      <description>Alternative definitions of “sovereignty” and “security” are emerging in the post-Cold War period. Scholars must update their interpretations of the words to be more inclusive if we are to reduce the vulnerability and increase the resilience of Arctic societies.</description>
